#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.5.42"
msgid "anupasampannassa—"
msgstr "if a monk says to a person who is not fully ordained,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.5.43"
msgid "“yena te vihāro paribhutto … pe … yena te cīvaraṃ paribhuttaṃ, yena te piṇḍapāto paribhutto, yena te senāsanaṃ paribhuttaṃ, yena te gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhāro paribhutto so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji, samāpajjati, samāpanno;"
msgstr "“The monk who has made use of your dwelling … who has made use of your robe-cloth … who has made use of your almsfood … who has made use of your dwelling … who has made use of your medicines attained the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling … is attaining … has attained …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.5.44"
msgid "so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthassa jhānassa lābhī, vasī;"
msgstr "obtains … masters …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.5.45"
msgid "tena bhikkhunā suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ sacchikatan”ti bhaṇantassa āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "has realized the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling,” he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc73, ms2V_292
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.5.46"
msgid "Āroceyyāti"
msgstr "Tells:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.5.47"
msgid "anupasampannassa—"
msgstr "if a monk says to a person who is not fully ordained,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.5.48"
msgid "“yaṃ tvaṃ āgamma vihāraṃ adāsi … pe … cīvaraṃ adāsi, piṇḍapātaṃ adāsi, senāsanaṃ adāsi, gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhāraṃ adāsi so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji, samāpajjati, samāpanno;"
msgstr "“The monk to whom you gave a dwelling … to whom you gave robe-cloth … to whom you gave almsfood … to whom you gave a dwelling … to whom you gave medicines … he attained the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling … is attaining … has attained …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.5.49"
msgid "so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthassa jhānassa lābhī, vasī;"
msgstr "obtains … masters …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.5.50"
msgid "tena bhikkhunā suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ sacchikatan”ti bhaṇantassa āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "has realized the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling,” he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. HTML: </span></p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.6.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc74, pts-cs-bu-pc8.2.6, ms2V_293
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.6.1"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.6.2"
msgid "upasampannassa, bhūtaṃ āroceti,"
msgstr "if he truthfully tells one who is fully ordained;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.6.3"
msgid "ādikammikassāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. HTML: </p><hr><p class="endsutta">
#. REF: sc75, ms2V_294
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:2.6.4"
msgid "Bhūtārocanasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr "The eighth rule, the training rule on telling truthfully, is finished."
